"{\"uid\": \"theconversation.com-anatomy-of-a-wave-what-makes-the-olympic-surf-break-at-teahupoo-unique-and-so-challenging-235301\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Honorary Senior Lecturer, Department of Civil and Environmental Engineering, University of Auckland, Waipapa Taumata Rau Tom Shand is affiliated with the Engineering Consultancy Tonkin + Taylor and with the industry association PIANC (World Association for Waterborne Transport Infrastructure).\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 295, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 117, \"end\": 120, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rau\", \"score\": 0.9999986523644097, \"rank\": 1.3475232457102608e-06, \"text\": \"Rau\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rau\"}, {\"begin\": 122, \"end\": 131, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Shand\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tom Shand\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Shand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Shand\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Honorary Senior Lecturer\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 24}, {\"ngram\": \"Department\", \"from\": 26, \"to\": 36}, {\"ngram\": \"Civil and Environmental Engineering\", \"from\": 40, \"to\": 75}, {\"ngram\": \"University\", \"from\": 77, \"to\": 87}, {\"ngram\": \"Auckland\", \"from\": 91, \"to\": 99}, {\"ngram\": \"the Engineering Consultancy Tonkin\", \"from\": 150, \"to\": 184}, {\"ngram\": \"Taylor\", \"from\": 187, \"to\": 193}, {\"ngram\": \"the industry association PIANC\", \"from\": 203, \"to\": 233}, {\"ngram\": \"(World Association\", \"from\": 234, \"to\": 252}, {\"ngram\": \"Waterborne Transport Infrastructure\", \"from\": 257, \"to\": 292}]}, {\"sentence\": \"University of Auckland, Waipapa Taumata Rauprovides funding as a member of The Conversation NZ.\", \"from\": 299, \"to\": 394, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"University\", \"from\": 299, \"to\": 309}, {\"ngram\": \"Auckland\", \"from\": 313, \"to\": 321}, {\"ngram\": \"Waipapa Taumata Rauprovides funding\", \"from\": 323, \"to\": 358}, {\"ngram\": \"a member\", \"from\": 362, \"to\": 370}, {\"ngram\": \"The Conversation NZ\", \"from\": 374, \"to\": 393}]}, {\"sentence\": \"University of Aucklandprovides funding as a member of The Conversation AU.\", \"from\": 396, \"to\": 470, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"University\", \"from\": 396, \"to\": 406}, {\"ngram\": \"Aucklandprovides\", \"from\": 410, \"to\": 426}, {\"ngram\": \"a member\", \"from\": 438, \"to\": 446}, {\"ngram\": \"The Conversation AU\", \"from\": 450, \"to\": 469}]}, {\"sentence\": \"View all partners https://doi.org/10.64628/AA.htsmagjpn Share article Print article As the Olympics get going in earnest this week, not everyone's attention is focused on host city Paris.\", \"from\": 472, \"to\": 663, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 657, \"end\": 662, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999175363313, \"rank\": 8.246373771466946e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all partners\", \"from\": 477, \"to\": 489}, {\"ngram\": \"Share article Print article\", \"from\": 528, \"to\": 555}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 559, \"to\": 571}, {\"ngram\": \"earnest\", \"from\": 585, \"to\": 592}, {\"ngram\": \"not everyone's attention\", \"from\": 604, \"to\": 628}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Surf fans are heading to Tahiti, half a world away in French Polynesia.\", \"from\": 664, \"to\": 735, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 689, \"end\": 695, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9973419008078123, \"rank\": 0.002665183514556378, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}, {\"begin\": 725, \"end\": 734, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\", \"score\": 0.9868006006778147, \"rank\": 0.013375953878807117, \"text\": \"Polynesia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Surf fans\", \"from\": 664, \"to\": 673}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Why?\", \"from\": 737, \"to\": 741, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Well, apart from the French coast resembling a lake at this time of year, on the south-west coast of Tahiti Iti is a wave unlike any other on the planet: Teahupo'o, which translates somewhat ominously as \\\"place of skulls\\\".\", \"from\": 742, \"to\": 964, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 763, \"end\": 769, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9979045731594878, \"rank\": 0.0020098075186687605, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lake\", \"from\": 787, \"to\": 793}, {\"ngram\": \"this time\", \"from\": 797, \"to\": 806}, {\"ngram\": \"year\", \"from\": 810, \"to\": 814}, {\"ngram\": \"the south-west coast\", \"from\": 819, \"to\": 839}, {\"ngram\": \"Tahiti\", \"from\": 843, \"to\": 849}, {\"ngram\": \"Iti\", \"from\": 850, \"to\": 853}, {\"ngram\": \"a wave\", \"from\": 857, \"to\": 863}, {\"ngram\": \"the planet\", \"from\": 884, \"to\": 894}, {\"ngram\": \"Teahupo'o\", \"from\": 896, \"to\": 905}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 947, \"to\": 952}, {\"ngram\": \"skulls\", \"from\": 956, \"to\": 962}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The wave is unique in the way it breaks.\", \"from\": 966, \"to\": 1006, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The wave\", \"from\": 966, \"to\": 974}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 988, \"to\": 995}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The lower part of the wave appears to drop away below sea level, with the top half folding over dramatically to create an almost cartoonishly perfect form.\", \"from\": 1007, \"to\": 1162, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The lower part\", \"from\": 1007, \"to\": 1021}, {\"ngram\": \"the wave\", \"from\": 1025, \"to\": 1033}, {\"ngram\": \"sea level\", \"from\": 1061, \"to\": 1070}, {\"ngram\": \"the top half\", \"from\": 1077, \"to\": 1089}, {\"ngram\": \"an almost cartoonishly perfect form\", \"from\": 1126, \"to\": 1161}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is both the weight of water in the plunging lip and the risk of injury or death for a surfer in the wrong position that make this one of the world's heaviest waves (in both senses of the word).\", \"from\": 1164, \"to\": 1360, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the weight\", \"from\": 1175, \"to\": 1185}, {\"ngram\": \"water\", \"from\": 1189, \"to\": 1194}, {\"ngram\": \"the plunging lip\", \"from\": 1198, \"to\": 1214}, {\"ngram\": \"the risk\", \"from\": 1219, \"to\": 1227}, {\"ngram\": \"injury\", \"from\": 1231, \"to\": 1237}, {\"ngram\": \"death\", \"from\": 1241, \"to\": 1246}, {\"ngram\": \"a surfer\", \"from\": 1251, \"to\": 1259}, {\"ngram\": \"the wrong position\", \"from\": 1263, \"to\": 1281}, {\"ngram\": \"the world's heaviest waves\", \"from\": 1304, \"to\": 1330}, {\"ngram\": \"both senses\", \"from\": 1335, \"to\": 1346}, {\"ngram\": \"the word\", \"from\": 1350, \"to\": 1358}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To understand why the wave breaks like this, we need to start withbathymetry: the shape of the seabed that influences waves as they approach the shore.\", \"from\": 1362, \"to\": 1513, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the wave\", \"from\": 1380, \"to\": 1388}, {\"ngram\": \"withbathymetry\", \"from\": 1424, \"to\": 1438}, {\"ngram\": \"the shape\", \"from\": 1440, \"to\": 1449}, {\"ngram\": \"the seabed\", \"from\": 1453, \"to\": 1463}, {\"ngram\": \"waves\", \"from\": 1480, \"to\": 1485}, {\"ngram\": \"the shore\", \"from\": 1503, \"to\": 1512}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At Teahupo'o, acombination of factorscomes into play.\", \"from\": 1514, \"to\": 1567, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"acombination\", \"from\": 1528, \"to\": 1540}, {\"ngram\": \"factorscomes\", \"from\": 1544, \"to\": 1556}, {\"ngram\": \"play\", \"from\": 1562, \"to\": 1566}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Waves arriving at Teahupo'o generally originate from intense \\\"roaring forties\\\" storm systems south of New Zealand.\", \"from\": 1569, \"to\": 1683, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1671, \"end\": 1682, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8282313449332459, \"rank\": 0.1420817944772724, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Waves\", \"from\": 1569, \"to\": 1574}, {\"ngram\": \"Teahupo'o\", \"from\": 1587, \"to\": 1596}, {\"ngram\": \"intense \\\"roaring forties\", \"from\": 1622, \"to\": 1646}, {\"ngram\": \"storm systems\", \"from\": 1648, \"to\": 1661}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By the time the waves reach Tahiti they have become ordered swell, with wave heights of two to five metres and periods of 14 to 20 seconds between successive waves.\", \"from\": 1684, \"to\": 1848, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1712, \"end\": 1718, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9973419008078123, \"rank\": 0.002665183514556378, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 1687, \"to\": 1695}, {\"ngram\": \"the waves\", \"from\": 1696, \"to\": 1705}, {\"ngram\": \"wave heights\", \"from\": 1756, \"to\": 1768}, {\"ngram\": \"two to five metres\", \"from\": 1772, \"to\": 1790}, {\"ngram\": \"periods\", \"from\": 1795, \"to\": 1802}, {\"ngram\": \"14 to 20 seconds\", \"from\": 1806, \"to\": 1822}, {\"ngram\": \"successive waves\", \"from\": 1831, \"to\": 1847}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These types of long-period waves normally start interacting with the seabed at depths of around 200 metres.\", \"from\": 1850, \"to\": 1957, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"These types\", \"from\": 1850, \"to\": 1861}, {\"ngram\": \"long-period waves\", \"from\": 1865, \"to\": 1882}, {\"ngram\": \"the seabed\", \"from\": 1915, \"to\": 1925}, {\"ngram\": \"depths\", \"from\": 1929, \"to\": 1935}, {\"ngram\": \"around 200 metres\", \"from\": 1939, \"to\": 1956}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On most coasts, this depth would occur up to several kilometres offshore.\", \"from\": 1958, \"to\": 2031, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"most coasts\", \"from\": 1961, \"to\": 1972}, {\"ngram\": \"this depth\", \"from\": 1974, \"to\": 1984}, {\"ngram\": \"several kilometres\", \"from\": 2003, \"to\": 2021}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But at Teahupo'o, it is much closer, just a couple of hundred metres.\", \"from\": 2032, \"to\": 2101, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just a couple of hundred metres\", \"from\": 2069, \"to\": 2100}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This rapid change in depth forces the wave to \\\"shoal\\\" very quickly - the wave speed slows, the distance between waves compresses and the wave height increases.\", \"from\": 2103, \"to\": 2262, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This rapid change\", \"from\": 2103, \"to\": 2120}, {\"ngram\": \"depth forces\", \"from\": 2124, \"to\": 2136}, {\"ngram\": \"the wave\", \"from\": 2137, \"to\": 2145}, {\"ngram\": \"the wave speed\", \"from\": 2172, \"to\": 2186}, {\"ngram\": \"the distance\", \"from\": 2194, \"to\": 2206}, {\"ngram\": \"the wave height increases\", \"from\": 2236, \"to\": 2261}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The change is so abrupt that the wave is still very linear - it has not had time to develop the peaked crest and flat trough (the lowest part of the wave) typical of waves in shallow water.\", \"from\": 2264, \"to\": 2453, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The change\", \"from\": 2264, \"to\": 2274}, {\"ngram\": \"the wave\", \"from\": 2293, \"to\": 2301}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 2340, \"to\": 2344}, {\"ngram\": \"the peaked crest\", \"from\": 2356, \"to\": 2372}, {\"ngram\": \"flat trough\", \"from\": 2377, \"to\": 2388}, {\"ngram\": \"the lowest part\", \"from\": 2390, \"to\": 2405}, {\"ngram\": \"the wave\", \"from\": 2409, \"to\": 2417}, {\"ngram\": \"waves\", \"from\": 2430, \"to\": 2435}, {\"ngram\": \"shallow water\", \"from\": 2439, \"to\": 2452}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Waves breaking on this type of steep slope would typically collapse, breaking from the middle of the wave and creating an unsurfable mess.\", \"from\": 2455, \"to\": 2593, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Waves\", \"from\": 2455, \"to\": 2460}, {\"ngram\": \"this type\", \"from\": 2473, \"to\": 2482}, {\"ngram\": \"steep slope\", \"from\": 2486, \"to\": 2497}, {\"ngram\": \"the middle\", \"from\": 2538, \"to\": 2548}, {\"ngram\": \"the wave\", \"from\": 2552, \"to\": 2560}, {\"ngram\": \"an unsurfable mess\", \"from\": 2574, \"to\": 2592}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But this does not happen.\", \"from\": 2594, \"to\": 2619, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At around ten metres' depth, a flatter shelf in the reef allows the wave to stabilise and \\\"stand up\\\" with a steep front face, before finally breaking as the reef rises again.\", \"from\": 2621, \"to\": 2795, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"around ten metres' depth\", \"from\": 2624, \"to\": 2648}, {\"ngram\": \"a flatter shelf\", \"from\": 2650, \"to\": 2665}, {\"ngram\": \"the reef\", \"from\": 2669, \"to\": 2677}, {\"ngram\": \"the wave\", \"from\": 2685, \"to\": 2693}, {\"ngram\": \"a steep front face\", \"from\": 2727, \"to\": 2745}, {\"ngram\": \"the reef\", \"from\": 2774, \"to\": 2782}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And break it does.\", \"from\": 2797, \"to\": 2815, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Owing to the linearity, there is far more water in the crest (the part above water) then most waves, and a deeper trough in front.\", \"from\": 2816, \"to\": 2946, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the linearity\", \"from\": 2825, \"to\": 2838}, {\"ngram\": \"far more water\", \"from\": 2849, \"to\": 2863}, {\"ngram\": \"the crest\", \"from\": 2867, \"to\": 2876}, {\"ngram\": \"the part\", \"from\": 2878, \"to\": 2886}, {\"ngram\": \"water\", \"from\": 2893, \"to\": 2898}, {\"ngram\": \"most waves\", \"from\": 2905, \"to\": 2915}, {\"ngram\": \"a deeper trough\", \"from\": 2921, \"to\": 2936}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 2940, \"to\": 2945}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This makes for the characteristic below-sea-level break at Teahupo'o, with the overturning lip being half the wave height, and a jet of compressed air forced out of the wave's barrel after breaking.\", \"from\": 2948, \"to\": 3146, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sea-level\", \"from\": 2988, \"to\": 2997}, {\"ngram\": \"Teahupo'o\", \"from\": 3007, \"to\": 3016}, {\"ngram\": \"the overturning lip\", \"from\": 3023, \"to\": 3042}, {\"ngram\": \"half the wave height\", \"from\": 3049, \"to\": 3069}, {\"ngram\": \"a jet\", \"from\": 3075, \"to\": 3080}, {\"ngram\": \"compressed air\", \"from\": 3084, \"to\": 3098}, {\"ngram\": \"the wave's barrel\", \"from\": 3113, \"to\": 3130}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The larger the wave, the closer to the steep offshore ramp it breaks, and the more extreme the plunging.\", \"from\": 3148, \"to\": 3252, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The larger the wave\", \"from\": 3148, \"to\": 3167}, {\"ngram\": \"the steep offshore ramp\", \"from\": 3183, \"to\": 3206}, {\"ngram\": \"the more extreme the plunging\", \"from\": 3222, \"to\": 3251}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A range of other unique features contribute to the way the wave breaks at Teahupo'o - and what makes it so challenging as a surfing wave.\", \"from\": 3254, \"to\": 3391, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A range\", \"from\": 3254, \"to\": 3261}, {\"ngram\": \"other unique features\", \"from\": 3265, \"to\": 3286}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 3301, \"to\": 3308}, {\"ngram\": \"the wave\", \"from\": 3309, \"to\": 3317}, {\"ngram\": \"a surfing wave\", \"from\": 3376, \"to\": 3390}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A deep channel runs alongside the shallow reef shelf.\", \"from\": 3393, \"to\": 3446, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A deep channel runs\", \"from\": 3393, \"to\": 3412}, {\"ngram\": \"the shallow reef shelf\", \"from\": 3423, \"to\": 3445}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The wave does not break in this deeper area, allowing it to peel - to break in one direction (in this case towards the left looking towards the shore) - and enabling surfers to ride the wave before it finally closes out onto shallow reef.\", \"from\": 3447, \"to\": 3685, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The wave\", \"from\": 3447, \"to\": 3455}, {\"ngram\": \"this deeper area\", \"from\": 3474, \"to\": 3490}, {\"ngram\": \"one direction\", \"from\": 3526, \"to\": 3539}, {\"ngram\": \"this case\", \"from\": 3544, \"to\": 3553}, {\"ngram\": \"the shore\", \"from\": 3587, \"to\": 3596}, {\"ngram\": \"surfers\", \"from\": 3613, \"to\": 3620}, {\"ngram\": \"the wave\", \"from\": 3629, \"to\": 3637}, {\"ngram\": \"shallow reef\", \"from\": 3672, \"to\": 3684}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A part of the shallow reef platform extends offshore, into the reef pass.\", \"from\": 3687, \"to\": 3760, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A part\", \"from\": 3687, \"to\": 3693}, {\"ngram\": \"the shallow reef platform\", \"from\": 3697, \"to\": 3722}, {\"ngram\": \"the reef pass\", \"from\": 3746, \"to\": 3759}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This shallow area bends and focuses wave energy from the wider, deeper part of the wave back into the breaking wave.\", \"from\": 3761, \"to\": 3877, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This shallow area bends\", \"from\": 3761, \"to\": 3784}, {\"ngram\": \"wave energy\", \"from\": 3797, \"to\": 3808}, {\"ngram\": \"the wider, deeper part\", \"from\": 3814, \"to\": 3836}, {\"ngram\": \"the wave\", \"from\": 3840, \"to\": 3848}, {\"ngram\": \"the breaking wave\", \"from\": 3859, \"to\": 3876}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This happens particularly on more westerly orientated swells, increasing the intensity of breaking.\", \"from\": 3878, \"to\": 3977, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more westerly orientated swells\", \"from\": 3907, \"to\": 3938}, {\"ngram\": \"the intensity\", \"from\": 3951, \"to\": 3964}, {\"ngram\": \"breaking\", \"from\": 3968, \"to\": 3976}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As well as this, the Teahupo'o wave breaks in a direction nearly opposite to the prevailing trade winds, keeping the wave face smooth.\", \"from\": 3979, \"to\": 4113, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a direction\", \"from\": 4025, \"to\": 4036}, {\"ngram\": \"the prevailing trade winds\", \"from\": 4056, \"to\": 4082}, {\"ngram\": \"the wave\", \"from\": 4092, \"to\": 4100}, {\"ngram\": \"face\", \"from\": 4101, \"to\": 4105}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A low tidal range also limits the times the reef is too deep or too shallow to surf.\", \"from\": 4115, \"to\": 4199, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A low tidal range\", \"from\": 4115, \"to\": 4132}, {\"ngram\": \"the times\", \"from\": 4145, \"to\": 4154}, {\"ngram\": \"the reef\", \"from\": 4155, \"to\": 4163}, {\"ngram\": \"surf\", \"from\": 4194, \"to\": 4198}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And the wave is near the Passa Hava'e reef pass, which helps the wave's focusing and breaking.\", \"from\": 4200, \"to\": 4294, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4225, \"end\": 4230, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Passa,_Pyr\\u00e9n\\u00e9es-Orientales\", \"score\": 0.9999999954807208, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Passa\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Passa,_Pyr\\u00e9n\\u00e9es-Orientales\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Passa,_Pyr\\u00e9n\\u00e9es-Orientales\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the wave\", \"from\": 4204, \"to\": 4212}, {\"ngram\": \"the wave\", \"from\": 4261, \"to\": 4269}, {\"ngram\": \"breaking\", \"from\": 4285, \"to\": 4293}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But because it is not right in the pass, the wave is not affected by high tidal or wave-induced currents.\", \"from\": 4295, \"to\": 4400, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the pass\", \"from\": 4326, \"to\": 4334}, {\"ngram\": \"the wave\", \"from\": 4336, \"to\": 4344}, {\"ngram\": \"high tidal or wave-induced currents\", \"from\": 4364, \"to\": 4399}]}, {\"sentence\": \"New-generation wave models that simulate individual waves, rather than just average energy density, provide insight into what creates a surf break such as Teahupo'o (see figure below).\", \"from\": 4402, \"to\": 4586, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"New-generation wave models\", \"from\": 4402, \"to\": 4428}, {\"ngram\": \"individual waves\", \"from\": 4443, \"to\": 4459}, {\"ngram\": \"just average energy density\", \"from\": 4473, \"to\": 4500}, {\"ngram\": \"insight\", \"from\": 4510, \"to\": 4517}, {\"ngram\": \"a surf break\", \"from\": 4536, \"to\": 4548}, {\"ngram\": \"Teahupo'o\", \"from\": 4557, \"to\": 4566}, {\"ngram\": \"figure\", \"from\": 4572, \"to\": 4578}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These models provide insight into what happens as waves shoal and refract (bend and focus) over the seabed as they approach break point.\", \"from\": 4587, \"to\": 4723, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"These models\", \"from\": 4587, \"to\": 4599}, {\"ngram\": \"insight\", \"from\": 4608, \"to\": 4615}, {\"ngram\": \"waves\", \"from\": 4637, \"to\": 4642}, {\"ngram\": \"the seabed\", \"from\": 4683, \"to\": 4693}, {\"ngram\": \"break point\", \"from\": 4711, \"to\": 4722}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They also significantly improve our understanding of what makes a particular surf break unique.\", \"from\": 4725, \"to\": 4820, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our understanding\", \"from\": 4757, \"to\": 4774}, {\"ngram\": \"a particular surf\", \"from\": 4789, \"to\": 4806}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This can help in assessing the potential impact of human or natural modifications to the environment.\", \"from\": 4821, \"to\": 4922, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the potential impact\", \"from\": 4848, \"to\": 4868}, {\"ngram\": \"human or natural modifications\", \"from\": 4872, \"to\": 4902}, {\"ngram\": \"the environment\", \"from\": 4906, \"to\": 4921}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Copyright \\u00a9 2010-2025,The Conversation Media Group Ltd\", \"from\": 4924, \"to\": 4978, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Copyright \\u00a9\", \"from\": 4924, \"to\": 4935}, {\"ngram\": \"Conversation Media Group Ltd\", \"from\": 4950, \"to\": 4978}]}]}"